item.title: About
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
[caption id="fullImg" align="aligncenter" width="580" caption="about txGarage"][/caption]

At txGarage we are dedicated to Texas and the auto world. We share news, thoughts, reviews, and more from Texas car enthusiasts. We are the hub for Texas car news. We look at everyday cars and sports cars that you would see in the garage of any number of your neighbors or in your neighborhood. We want to show off the talents and enthusiasm that lives in Texas and joins us in our passion for everything auto related.

Follow us on: Twitter - YouTube - RSS - and on Facebook

Help us keep great content and improved video! If you own a local business in Texas or know someone who does, let them know about advertising with txGarage!

We currently work with some great local companies and love meeting and supporting local small, or big, businesses! The process is simple and competitively priced. Contact us through the contact form in the Footer.

Thanks for your support!

item.title: Contact
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Looking to contact txGarage? Check in the footer for our Contact Form!

Looking to be included as a sponsor, advertiser, preferred dealer, or preferred shops? Also use the contact form below and add the corresponding subject.

Know someone in Texas with an awesome ride that we should feature? Hit us up either in the contact form or on one of our many social networks.

We're here to answer questions you may have, so feel free to be sociable and hit us up anytime. If we don't respond quickly enough by email, find us on Twitter or Facebook!

txGarage - News, Thoughts, Reviews - for Texas car enthusiasts. Lots of great photos and reviews of car for Texas car enthusiasts, buy Texas car enthusiasts from txGarage.com.




txGarage-3-12

By Adam Moore in txGarage

12 pages

Looking for a new way to enjoy txGarage articles? You can now order a magazine with some of our top reviews and more behind the scenes info about txGarage. The magazine is offered in full print (that includes a digital copy) or only as a digital copy. This is great for local dealers or shops who are looking for some great, local content for waiting rooms!

You can pick up a copy today for a reasonable price and a digital copy is even cheaper!

We will be publishing txGarage Magazine in monthly issues as long as we're getting good feedback. So jump on and order some today!

If you are a Texas based business who is interested in advertising with txGarage please email us at contact@txgarage.com.
